{
  "stem": "20616.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he was told, well, you don't give free brushes out when you ring the doorbell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You tell the housewife, he says, I'm a Fuller Brush Man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I have a free sample for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that was the in to get into the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But he was taught the free samples would have to be on the bottom of his case.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "In order to get to the free samples, he would have to show all and demonstrate all the different brushes and mops and things that they had.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he did that for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was not a good way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You couldn't make a living from it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But he made a few cents here and there that way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And my mother, she became a, a cleaning lady and with very little experience.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "She was much too slow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Then she-- in the summer time, she went to the beach and sold ice cream at the beach.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I was-- I found out later I was sent to a camp for underprivileged children because they wanted to have me out of the way while they were looking for a job and-- or actually working for, on some sort of a job, if you could call it that.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So through some sort of a Jewish federation, they send me to a summer camp for eight weeks, which probably was the best thing that could happen for me, to me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I learned to play baseball.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned the language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I learned the language as I wasn't supposed to learn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was-- I, I-- my English after those eight weeks were so much better.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later on, when I went back to school again, I did very well in school.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
